# Rivermarsh Development

## Package Overview

Mobile-first 3D exploration game with React Three Fiber + Capacitor.

## Commands

```bash
pnpm install           # Install deps
pnpm run dev           # Dev server
pnpm run build         # Production build
pnpm run test          # Run tests
pnpm run cap:sync:android  # Sync Android
pnpm run cap:open:android  # Open Android Studio
```

## Key Patterns

- Mobile-first responsive design
- ECS architecture with Miniplex
- React Three Fiber for 3D
- Zustand for state management
- strata for procedural effects (pending integration)
